category: Python
build-depends: cygport 
sdesc: "Python AST that abstracts the underlying Python version"
ldesc: "A generic AST to represent Python2 and Python3's Abstract Syntax Tree(AST).
GAST provides a compatibility layer between the AST of various Python versions, as produced by ast.parse from the standard ast module."
skip:

homepage: https://github.com/serge-sans-paille/gast/
